If the last year and a half has taught us anything, it’s that it is vital to manage our stress daily. Soaking in a hot bath can quickly ease tension, regulate breathing, boost blood flow and reduce inflammation and pain in muscles and joints – all of which is good for the immune system. It can also help to calm the nervous system and quieten the mind – especially when you add elements such as soothing music, soft lighting and aromatherapy to create a tranquil environment. Here are some tips to ensure success: Enjoy!